{"chapter_number":95,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":28,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"التين","name_complex":"At-Tīn","name_simple":"At-Tin","verses_count":8,"pages":[597,597],"meaning":{"text":"The Fig","en":"The Fig","id":"Buah Tin"},"verses":[[[1,6099,"95:1","وَالتِّينِ وَالزَّيْتُونِ",["I swear by the fig and the olive,","Demi (buah) Tin dan (buah) Zaitun,"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[2,6100,"95:2","وَطُورِ سِينِينَ",["And mount Sinai,","demi gunung Sinai,"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[3,6101,"95:3","وَهَٰذَا الْبَلَدِ الْأَمِينِ",["And this city made secure,","dan demi negeri (Mekah) yang aman ini."],597,30,60,239,null,null],[4,6102,"95:4","لَقَدْ خَلَقْنَا الْإِنسَانَ فِي أَحْسَنِ تَقْوِيمٍ",["Certainly We created man in the best make.","Sungguh, Kami telah menciptakan manusia dalam bentuk yang sebaik-baiknya,"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[5,6103,"95:5","ثُمَّ رَدَدْنَاهُ أَسْفَلَ سَافِلِينَ",["Then We render him the lowest of the low.","kemudian Kami kembalikan dia ke tempat yang serendah-rendahnya,"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[6,6104,"95:6","إِلَّا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحَاتِ فَلَهُمْ أَجْرٌ غَيْرُ مَمْنُونٍ",["Except those who believe and do good, so they shall have a reward never to be cut off.","kecuali orang-orang yang beriman dan mengerjakan kebajikan; maka mereka akan mendapat pahala yang tidak ada putus-putusnya."],597,30,60,239,null,null],[7,6105,"95:7","فَمَا يُكَذِّبُكَ بَعْدُ بِالدِّينِ",["Then who can give you the lie after (this) about the judgment?","Maka apa yang menyebabkan (mereka) mendustakanmu (tentang) hari pembalasan setelah (adanya keterangan-keterangan) itu?"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[8,6106,"95:8","أَلَيْسَ اللَّهُ بِأَحْكَمِ الْحَاكِمِينَ",["Is not Allah the best of the Judges?","Bukankah Allah hakim yang paling adil?"],597,30,60,239,null,null]],[[[1,3,597,"&#xfb51;","word","وَالتِّينِ",["By the fig",""]],[2,3,597,"&#xfb52;","word","وَالزَّيْتُونِ",["and the olive",""]],[3,3,597,"&#xfb53;","end","ﭓ",[nul